title: Elmoadab Tabriz F.C.
text:
Elmoadab Tabriz Football Club (, "Bashgah-e Futbal-e Elmuadab Tebriz") is an Iranian <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Tabriz">Tabriz</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a> who compete in <a href="Azadegan%20League">Azadegan League</a>.
The club bought the licence of <a href="Shahrdari%20Tabriz%20F.C.">Shahrdari Tabriz</a> in <a href="Azadegan%20League">Azadegan League</a> in 2019.
